dialogue = Array[String](["This prison of problems scares me off, 
The darkness says I’m done.
", "But the sunshine behind the bars,
That comes from the sun,", "Tells me again and again,
And it’s true I bet,", "It is not over yet.", "I know I am right,
I can prove it easily.", "I must get my life again,
I know I must rise again.", "By the fear of struggle, in a pit,
Made of hopelessness, I’m bound.", "But from the heavens on the other side,
I hear a silent sound.", "It gives me a feeling once again,
That the whole world is with me,", "And I think I as well should be. ", "I might need to work so hard, 
I will do it easily.", "I must get my life again,
", "I know I must rise again.", "I read this poem in a book once.....", "I think it was titled \"Trinkets by Krishna Gupta\" 
", "Available on Amazon in UK, USA and India"])

